data.title: Una Martone - LEADERSHIP HARRISBURG AREA
data.meta_description: My purpose is to help others see their best, be their best, and do their best.  Thankful… · Experience: LEADERSHIP HARRISBURG AREA · Location: Harrisburg · 500+ connections on LinkedIn. View Una Martone’s profile on LinkedIn, a professional community of 1 billion members.
data.text:
“Una is an amazing talent and asset to Leadership Harrisburg. Her tireless leadership within the organization, devotion to the region, and position as role model to servant leaders everywhere makes her an exceptional leader.”

“Una Martone eptomizes all the characteristics one would like to see in a development executive and leader. Compassion, empathy, and she listens to the ideas of others. She is quick to compliment colleagues, donors or volunteers on a job well done. Finally, she always looks out for others and goes beyond the call of duty in achieving goals that will help improve their lives. Honesty, integrity and a true sense of humanity best describe her good work.”
